609
00:27:12.498 --> 00:27:17.236
I think it left a very.
very bitter taste in his mouth.

610
00:27:17.236 --> 00:27:19.838
Yes. I think it did.

611
00:27:19.838 --> 00:27:23.475
He discovered that many
black students at Cornell.

612
00:27:23.475 --> 00:27:27.179
