1129
00:52:18.669 --> 00:52:20.304
And do you know what I just did?

1130
00:52:20.304 --> 00:52:22.873
I just listed the books
you've published

1131
00:52:22.873 --> 00:52:24.842
since turning 80.

1132
00:52:24.842 --> 00:52:26.143
[ Laughs ]

1133
00:52:26.143 --> 00:52:31.548
